Logger:

    Used to log the application activity

    diff btw logger and System.out.print [sop]:

        Sop:
            . output print in console
            . no message priority
        
        logger
            . logger output can be console, file, database
            . we can have  priority for the message 
                it uses log levels
            . It is easily pluglable, (we can add or remove easily simply by switch on/ of)

